#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:125
msgid ""
"Malnutrition follow-up (MNA re-scoring reminders, intake vs needs, "
"hydration) relies on the clinical registers and the care module. See [The "
"clinical registers](../soins/registres.md)."
msgstr ""
"De opvolging van ondervoeding (herinneringen om de MNA opnieuw te scoren, "
"inname vs behoeften, hydratatie) steunt op de klinische registers en de "
"zorgmodule. Zie [De klinische registers](../soins/registres.md)."

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:130
msgid "OHAT — oral health"
msgstr "OHAT — mondgezondheid"

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:132
msgid ""
"The **OHAT** (Oral Health Assessment Tool) assesses **oral health** across "
"**8 categories**, scored from 0 (healthy) to 2 (needs treatment): lips, "
"tongue, gums and tissues, saliva, natural teeth, dentures, oral cleanliness "
"and dental pain."
msgstr ""
"De **OHAT** (Oral Health Assessment Tool) beoordeelt de **mondgezondheid** "
"in **8 categorieën**, gescoord van 0 (gezond) tot 2 (te behandelen): lippen,"
" tong, tandvlees en weefsels, speeksel, natuurlijke tanden, prothesen, "
"mondhygiëne en tandpijn."

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:137
msgid ""
"The total ranges from 0 to 16. **Here, the higher the score, the more "
"concerning the situation.**"
msgstr ""
"Het totaal loopt van 0 tot 16. **Hier geldt: hoe hoger de score, hoe "
"zorgwekkender de situatie.**"

