msgid "Tinetti — balance, gait and fall risk"
msgstr "Tinetti — evenwicht, gang en valrisico"

#: ../../content/residents/evaluations.md:155
msgid ""
"The **Tinetti** scale (POMA) assesses **balance** and **gait** to estimate "
"**fall risk**:"
msgstr ""
"De **Tinetti-schaal** (POMA) beoordeelt het **evenwicht** en de **gang** om "
"het **valrisico** in te schatten:"

